  "description": "remove all the texture and sounds from minecraft",
  "body": "# no.\n\nThis resource pack removes all miecraft textures: buttons, fonts, menus, icons, and most of the UI. The game becomes nearly impossible to navigate because nothing is displayed anymore. This pack is not designed for gameplay — it is simply a minimal, empty, and fully stripped‑down experience.\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Warning\n\nThis pack also removes **all** UI elements, including:\n- Buttons  \n- Fonts\n- Click sounds\n\nBecause of this, you may not be able to access settings, menus, or even disable the pack normally (unless you're lucky to disable it).\n\nTo deactivate it, you must **rename the pack’s folder** so Minecraft cannot load it, or **delete the pack** from your resourcepacks directory.\n\nUse with caution.\n",
